# key-word-dot-prefix

## Input

```
.key value
a.b.c value2

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..24
  ENTRY@0..11
    WORD_KEY@0..4
      WORD@0..4 ".key"
    SPACE@4..5 " "
    LINE_STRING@5..10
      STRING@5..10 "value"
    NEWLINE@10..11 "\n"
  ENTRY@11..24
    WORD_KEY@11..16
      WORD@11..16 "a.b.c"
    SPACE@16..17 " "
    LINE_STRING@17..23
      STRING@17..23 "value2"
    NEWLINE@23..24 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..4 ".key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@5..10 "value",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@11..16 "a.b.c",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@17..23 "value2",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

